<h2>Styled Icons</h2>
<p>Icons can be styled directly using inline styles or passed attributes:</p>
<div class="icon-demo">
    <div class="icon-card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <LucideActivity style="color: #e74c3c; width: 48px; height: 48px;" />
        </div>
        <code>style="color: red; width: 48px;"</code>
    </div>

    <div class="icon-card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <LucideAirplay style="color: #3498db; width: 48px; height: 48px;" />
        </div>
        <code>style="color: blue; width: 48px;"</code>
    </div>

    <div class="icon-card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <LucideAlbum style="color: pink; width: 48px; height: 48px;" />
        </div>
        <code>style="color: pink; width: 48px;"</code>
    </div>
</div>

<h2>Icon Counts (Development Mode)</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Lucide Icons:</strong> 1,539 icons (currently enabled)</li>
    <li><strong>Note:</strong> Bootstrap and Material Design icons are disabled for faster development builds</li>
