</ul>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Fully Embedded:</strong> SVG content embedded in compiled code - No HTTP calls!</li>
    <li><strong>Fully Trimmable:</strong> Only icons you use are included in the published output</li>
    <li><strong>Fast Builds:</strong> 1-5 second build times with 11,000+ icons</li>
    <li><strong>Type-Safe:</strong> Full IntelliSense support</li>
    <li><strong>CSS Controllable:</strong> Style icons with standard CSS properties</li>
    <li><strong>Multiple Icon Sets:</strong> Lucide, Material Design, Bootstrap (11,064 total)</li>
    <li><strong>Zero Runtime Overhead:</strong> Build-time generation, no reflection</li>
    <li><strong>Zero Network Requests:</strong> No HttpClient or wwwroot files needed</li>
</ul>
